data.title: Episode 2549 (10 July 2003)
data.meta_description: Kat and Alfie's date goes badly. Patrick is devastated by Anthony's life-changing decision. Alfie Moon - Shane Richie Kat Slater - Jessie Wallace Doctor Anthony Trueman - Nicholas R. Bailey Paul Trueman - Gary Beadle Patrick Trueman - Rudolph Walker Spencer Moon - Christopher Parker Sharon Watts...
data.text:
Nana Moon and Spencer are concerned about Alfie. Alfie opens up to Phil about Kat and feels more positive. On their date, Alfie notices Kat smiling at a man and denies being jealous. Kat leaves when Alfie questions her about going back to Anthony's.

Anthony refuses to go to the pub with Patrick and Paul. He tells Paul he's jacking in his job. Later he announces to Patrick and Paul that he's going travelling.

Zoe tries to conceal her pain about Kelly and Ronny.

Pauline defends Den after a comment Dennis makes. Sharon is surprised that Dennis was interested in hearing about Den from Pauline, she later catches him looking at old photos but pretends not to notice.

Adi and Ronny question Dan about his mystery woman.

Janine attempts to charm Barry.
